-- ============================================
-- Test Topology: Two rings sharing junction node D(인제)
-- Ring 1: A(춘천) - B(남춘천) - C(화천) - D(인제) - E(양구) - F(홍천) - A
-- Ring 2: D(인제) - G(속초) - H(고성) - I(양양) - J(강릉) - K(평창) - D
-- Junction: 인제(D) connects both rings via 송광치 equipment
--
-- Each substation has: 1 송광치 (NETWORK) + 1 OFD
-- OFD connects to multiple FiberPaths via different port numbers
-- Port number = FiberPath number (both sides of a FP use the same port)
-- ============================================

